_-||VR_TRAINING_SPYRO||-_

Created by Spyro (CupoOci)

This is a map of virtual reality. In this map, the CTs and Ts have to spend 10 levels of this map. The first team to reach the final you can press a button that makes the winners going to a high place with guns and the losers are down.

The two teams will not be found until it reaches the end.

The map allows a maximum of 28 players per team.

But if you want you can practice on the map in single player.

Every three levels you get a check point, which means that when you fall do not have to return to level 1.

This is how it works:

1-Normal
2-Colour
3-Black
4-Normal (Checkpoint)
5-Colour
6-Black
7-Normal (Checkpoint)
8-Colour
9-Black
10-Last level (Checkpoint)

PLEASE COMMENT :/
